title: Gungala, The Virgin Of The Jungle, La Vergine Della Giungla 1967

sources.title: Gungala The Virgin Of The Jungle La Vergine Della Giungla
sources.description: Another Jungle Girl movie. This one featuring Kitty Swan as Gungala who has somehow become the white queen of an the Leopard men. At least she is not blonde.Â  Typical jungle movie of the time with lots of scenes of white guys with guns shooting natives armed with bows and arrows. Eventually most of the cast ends up dead with Gungala and her beau getting away with the diamonds.
